      <div class="row">
        <p>
          <ol>
            <li><strong>Download the CSV file.</strong></li>
            <li><strong>Sign-in to your Google Calendar.</strong> You can click <a href="http://calendar.google.com" target="_blank">here</a>. You will be redirected to Google Calendar.
            <li><strong>Create a new calendar.</strong> This will make sure that if you’re done or if you need to edit something in this work plan, it will be easy! To do this, simply go to your Calendars section on the left hand side, click the drop down icon, and select “Create Calendar.”</li>
            <li><strong>Import Calendar.</strong> On left hand side, you will see a group of calendars called “Other Calendars.” Click the drop down icon, and from there, select Import Calendar. Upload the CSV file. Select the calendar you just created.</li>
            <li><strong>DONE!</strong> You have your nice calendar created!</li>
